{
  "stem": "14810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it got less and less and less, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And fortunately for us, it was snowing, and we had utensils, so we could scoop up-- I had a piece of string and scooped up, while the train stopped slow, I scooped up the snow and-- and licked the snow.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That kept us alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Took us 10 days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Finally, we reached Nordhausen, which is an earlier concentration camp, and there they unloaded us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "From the 120 or 140, I don't know, there was 20 left of us. 20.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Every night, we just-- we just threw out-- you know, throw away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, we picked them up, but it was people just died in front of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember I talked to this fellow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We talked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We sat, and we talked, then all the sudden, he just keeled over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I looked at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He's dead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But that's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When we got to, finally, Nordhausen, we got to Nordhausen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember they unloaded us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I could hardly walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was-- those inmates had to help us to-- to walk to the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were in the camp in another 10 days there, and then they moved us again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The English came from another direction, so they moved us again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They put us again on trains, and this time they moved us to Thuringen, which is the-- Dora.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The name of the camp was Dora.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was in the mountains, Over there, they-- they-- where they used there V-1 and V-2 against England.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, it was the mountains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were there about six weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We worked in the inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We dynamited the inside, the mountains, and we built, you know, storage rooms and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
